metadata.description: [Star (Zvezdochka)](https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmVWtADBDz5sfTcRkjm4XJY8HEkztkMffRJQR366fjV3p2) is CosmicPaws’ 2nd-Genesis Muttniks NFT. The Muttniks are the pioneering canines who led the way for human exploration of space. Muttnik STAR was the last dog to launch to space before the first human being–legendary space hero Yuri Gagarin. Named with great affection by the cosmonaut himself, STAR went to space 18 days prior to Gagarin in the same spacecraft. Using the proprietary Do-Over Generating Engine (aka “the DOGE”) for minting, Cosmic Paws honors, celebrates, and evolves the original brave space heroes, bringing the Muttniks forward in time and into the present for future adventures with agency in the metaverse. For all Muttkind!
